  "title": "Mandarin Teacher",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conduct Chinese language lesson according to the teaching plan</li>\n  <li>Plan and development teaching materials</li>\n  <li>Chinese tutoring for students from Kindergarten 1 - Secondary 4</li>\n  <li>Able to connect with students and children well</li>\n  <li>Monitor and coaching student’s progress for feedback purpose</li>\n  <li>Engage effective communication with parents regularly on student’s progress</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma to Degree and above in Education/Chinese Language Teaching or equivalent</li>\n  <li>Must have teaching experience and in a classroom setting</li>\n  <li>Applicants must be passionate about education, responsible and self-motivated</li>\n  <li>Good classroom management skills</li>\n  <li>Committed to deliver lessons in excellence</li>\n  <li>Able to work closely with teaching staffs and parents</li>\n</ul>",
